{
  "texts": [
    "This skew is further compounded by the frequent absence of crucial metadata such as age and gender, adding to the problem of representation in datasets 47.",
    "Language barriers also shape the current development of the field.",
    "While tools like ChatGPT show proficiency in English, their accuracy in other languages can still be lacking 76.",
    "The resultant focus on English-centric social media platforms can overlook insights from non-English-speaking regions.",
    "Future research could gain from incorporating data from platforms prevalent in these areas to provide a more holistic view 31."
  ]
}